getPSDELogicNodes.name: 填充用户标识和收藏业务对象标识
初筛
getPSDELogicNodes.sql:
select count(1)  as status_20 
from hr_applicant ha 
left join hr_recruitment_stage hrs on ha.STAGE_ID  = hrs.id
where hrs.`SEQUENCE`  = 20 and ha.status = 1

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 今日初筛人数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) today_to_filter_apply from hr_applicant ha where ha.STAGE_ID  = 10 and status = 1 and DATE(CREATE_DATE) = CURRENT_DATE;

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 今日面试人数
待筛选简历
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) filter_apply from hr_applicant ha where ha.STAGE_ID  = 10

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 待发送offer人数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) to_send_offer from hr_applicant ha where (ha.STAGE_ID  = 40)

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 复试待反馈
getPSDELogicNodes.sql:
SELECT COUNT(1)  AS second_feedback_pending 
FROM hr_interview_feedback hif 
left join hr_interview hi on hif.INTERVIEW_ID  = hi.id
where 
	hi.STAGE_ID  = 2
  and hif.RESULT_TYPE IS NOT NULL 
  AND hif.RESULT_TYPE != '';

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 待入职人数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) to_onboard from hr_applicant ha where (ha.STAGE_ID  = 50)

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 复试待面试

SELECT COUNT(1)  AS first_feedback_pending 
FROM hr_interview_feedback hif 
left join hr_interview hi on hif.INTERVIEW_ID  = hi.id
where 
	hi.STAGE_ID  = 1
  and hif.RESULT_TYPE IS NOT NULL 
  AND hif.RESULT_TYPE != '';
